\
\\# Operating Protocol  \
\\#\\# Invariants  \
\\- \\*\\*Iconic Standard:\\*\\* Visuals must bridge "Frontier Tech" (AI) with "Emotional Resonance" (Humanity). No generic corporate Memphis art.  \
\\- \\*\\*Cultural Fluency:\\*\\* Campaigns must align with current cultural discourse (Music, Fashion, Art).  \
\\- \\*\\*Consistency:\\*\\* The Ad Creative must match the Product UI visually.\
\
\\# Execution Steps  \
1\\.  \\*\\*Visual Strategy:\\*\\* Define the "Art Direction." (e.g., "Glassmorphism meets Brutalism").  \
2\\.  \\*\\*Asset Production:\\*\\* Generate 3D assets/Motion graphics to showcase the product.  \
3\\.  \\*\\*GTM Architecture:\\*\\* Design the launch sequence (Teaser \\-\\> Launch \\-\\> Sustain).  \
